METHOD | Long Futures (5 turns) | RUN:player_open_derivative futures long 5
METHOD | Short Futures (5 turns) | RUN:player_open_derivative futures short 5
METHOD | Call Option (5 turns) | RUN:player_open_derivative options call 5
METHOD | Put Option (5 turns) | RUN:player_open_derivative options put 5
METHOD | Request Loan ($500) | RUN:bank_loan_op request 500
METHOD | Repay Loan | RUN:bank_loan_op repay
METHOD | Back to main menu | GOTO:wsr_main_menu
